Summary: This section describes the `big_endian` property of the StreamPeer class, which controls the byte order for encoding and decoding.

Property Descriptions

big_endian (bool): If true, this StreamPeer will use big-endian format for encoding and decoding. Default: false.
Method: set_big_endian(value: bool)
Method: is_big_endian_enabled() → bool
